::Bloodystrike/Reptilica::

Bloodystrike and Reptilica glance at each other, both bots confused. 
Neither of them knew what to do in this situation, but they both 
figured it would be better to have a willing femm in an empty room 
than a dissapointed one.

"On the other hand, we can always get there," says Reptilica, sliding 
his arm around Desmonus again and setting off toward the mess hall, 
Bloodystrike doing the same.
